Question 12 : Flatten binary tree to linked list

Leetcode : 114

Could have been solved using a List but it would have space Complexity of O(n).
So this soln has space Complexity of O(1) :
For each currentNode look for the rightmost node in the left subtree of that currentNode and attach the right subtree
of the currentNode to the rightmost node of the left subtree and then make the entire left subtree a right subtree and
make the left null.

